zktools

zktools is a collection of open Bash scripts designed for system security and system management within the Zero Knowledge Network (ZKN). These tools help automate security configurations, manage system resources, and enhance overall system integrity.

Features

Automates system security configurations

Provides system management utilities

Enhances security for Zero Knowledge Network environments

Streamlines administrative tasks

Installation

Clone the repository and set up executable permissions:

sudo apt update
sudo apt install libncurses-dev
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/zktools.git
cd zktools
chmod +x *
sudo cp * /usr/local/bin

Use "zktools" for main menu.

